wizernes_base_rc1

Wizernes_base is a remake of the map by the same name in Return to Castle Wolfenstein. The map features 32 spawn points, and a working radar file. 

You can play the map on the ** WOLFENSTEIN CONQUEST ** server at 205.234.203.82:27015

The map features a working nav, custom radar and some sounds.

To install, place the .bsp in your cstrike/maps folde

Download the deathmatch version from 
[here](http://dl.dropbox.com/u/1491682/Winzernes/dm_wizernes_base_rc1.rar "http://dl.dropbox.com/u/1491682/Winzernes/dm_wizernes_base_rc1.rar")
